01:28:17.081 --> 01:28:18.548
Dobro.

01:28:26.589 --> 01:28:28.450
Prosim, ne.

01:28:31.338 --> 01:28:33.282
Nič ti ne bom naredil.

01:28:38.737 --> 01:28:40.566
Lahko greš.

01:28:43.375 --> 01:28:45.464
Kam naj grem?

01:28:45.668 --> 01:28:47.773
Mož beseda sem.

01:28:48.057 --> 01:28:52.657
Povedal si po resnici,
zato ti bom dal možnost.

01:28:53.775 --> 01:28:59.190
Enako možnost, kot jo je imela ona.
